    "description": "A pie to write home about. You'll slow cook tender beef in red wine sauce with veggies, until rich and melt-in-the-mouth, then load onto golden mash spiked with cheddar and crispy onions. Slide it under the grill till bubbling, then serve with buttery green beans and Tenderstem Broccoli on the side.",
